A project for learning OpenGL

1. How to build glfw?
    On Windows:
        install cmake, ninja, msvc compiler toolset
        generate ninja build system(in cmd shell)
            cmd.exe /c "C:\Program Files\Microsoft Visual Studio\2022\Community\VC\Auxiliary\Build\vcvars64.bat" && CMake -B build -G "Ninja Multi-Config" -DCMAKE_EXPORT_COMPILE_COMMANDS=ON
        build debug lib
            cmake --build build --config Debug
        build release lib
            cmake --build build --config Release

